  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Buffet Breakfast each morning there is a continental buffet breakfast that includes a wide selection of sweet and savoury homemade produce, including hot options. There is a coffee bar available on request.</p>
<p>Half board options are available for a supplement. You'll have a four course menu with two choices for your first and second courses. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
