  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><u>Restaurants &amp; Bars</u></strong></p>
<p><strong>The restaurant</strong> is set in a spacious has a large terrace immersed in the citrus grove, perfect for dining al fresco. From the terrace you’ll have views of the sea. The kitchen serves a delicious an a la carte menu with typical Sicilian dishes, often made using the properties own produce grown on their land, including their olive oil and local wines.</p>
<p><strong>Bar</strong> with lounge area where guests can enjoy drinks and refreshments.</p>
<p><strong><u>Pools &amp; Beaches </u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Swimming Pool </strong>The large pool is surrounded by Italian gardens and has unrivaled views across the Baroque city of Noto.</p>
<p><strong>Beaches </strong>Located close to the coast (approx. 10 minute’s drive) where you’ll find beautiful sandy beaches and the clear Mediterranean sea.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Rooms </strong></p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are around 26m². All rooms are equipped with a television, wifi, mini-bar, bath or shower, safe and air conditioning.</p>
<p> </p>]]></facilityDescription>
