<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are around 26m². These spacious rooms are decorated in light, fresh tones and furnished with beautiful antiques. Rooms have double or twin beds and can sleep between two and four people. Rooms with a balcony are available on request, please call to book. </p>
